        <head xml:id="la30px-aaa303-Hd1e104">Proposition 2</head>
        <p xml:id="la30px-aaa303-d1e106">
          Proposition 3
        </p>
        <p xml:id="la30px-aaa303-d1e111">
          The Pope, by authority of his office, can and should name necessary and ideal ministers from all states of Christendom towards this end of preaching the Gospel. He can make these ministers accept this charge and office. The ministers are obligated to accept and obey him, as though obeying Christ himself.
        </p>
